_sText:
Gun Game map for Bastille Day, I give you the Champs Elysees! Its a small portion of the road, with the Arc de Triomphe at the top. Each starting side (in the grass) has two glass floor access's to the underground pathway.

I must warn you, the car lights are bright, nearly blinding even if staring directly into them, I wanted the deer in headlights feel and I think I achieved that. 

Download the file, save it in your counter strike map directory under C:/Program Files/Steam/Steamapps/"username"/Counter Strike-Source/CStrike/Maps
